snippet.title: Postmod Pod EP#2: Are the Royals Okay?
snippet.description:
Hey guys! We've created this podcast channel to share our Current Affairs Podcast content! We are Felipe and Lillian, Americans living in the UK, trying to make sense of this modern world. 

In this episode, we comment on the following topics:

https://youtu.be/o3fq4JpufVE
http://www.eviemagazine.com/post/amber-heard-investigated-perjury-johnny-depp-police-body-camera-footage
https://twitter.com/stillgray/status/1394857117559885826?s=21
https://twitter.com/kensingtonroyal/status/1395484854272335875?s=21
https://twitter.com/selfpaidkaio/status/1395363054959972353?s=21
https://twitter.com/mailplus/status/1395343695625564164?s=21
https://news.sky.com/story/harry-accuses-royal-family-of-total-silence-and-neglect-in-documentary-12312388

We hope you subscribe to our podcast and it doesn't result in this channel being banned!! Hit that notification bell, too.
